data.description: Welcome home to a spacious 3 bedroom/ 2 bath house at Sheffield Village. Floor plan features split bedrooms, large open kitchen with breakfast bar and separate dining area. Wood burning fireplace in the living room. Plenty of natural light inside.  Enjoy your morning coffee or a glass of wine after work in your backyard overlooking a pond. 2 car garage. Perfect location close to 335 acre Sheffired Regional Park, International Airport, highways,  River City Market Place, shopping, restaurants and entertainment. Community offers boat and RV parking. No CDD fees and very low HOA fee (only $89 for a whole year).
